txt.en: In the wake of the great host that passed through not long ago, straggling Uruks have set down a war-camp, and now sit atop the cliffs as masters of the Fords of Isen.
You have defeated a number of Uruks at the Fords of Isen, but the true danger marches by the tens of thousands towards Helm's Deep.
Saruman's Uruk-hai can be found at the north-east cliffs at the Fords of Isen in the Westfold.\n\nYou should defeat the Uruks that sit atop the Fords.
